4. Switch between branches
git switch main

| Command                             | Use Case                      |
| ----------------------------------- | ----------------------------- |
| `git switch -c new-branch`          | Create & switch to new branch |
| `git add .` + `git commit -m "msg"` | Save your work                |
| `git push -u origin branch-name`    | Upload branch to GitHub       |
| `git switch main`                   | Go back to main branch        |
| `git branch -d branch-name`         | Delete branch after merging   |
